Welcome to the new PlayMindCrack server! A bunch of us MindCrackers got together to try out some of the games on the PlayMindCrack server before its launch.

MindCrack: http://www.youtube.com/user/MindCrackNetwork
PlayMindCrack is a free to play public MindCrack server offering a variety of fun mini-games.
